# Always-on neural wake word — BASE (2026-07-04). The pretrained ONNX models ship
# in every wheel already; openwakeword + CPU onnxruntime are the tiny (~15 MB),
# torch-free runtime that runs them, so "Hey Jarvis" fires out-of-the-box on any
# machine incl. a headless CPU VPS. CPU onnxruntime is universal and NOT on the
# lockfile forbidden list (only torch/ctranslate2/faster-whisper/onnxruntime-gpu
# are). See pyproject.toml note.
